title: Maine Mini Golf Wrap Up
description:
Injuries and poor conditions didn't stop Kirk Minihane from putting on what's being described as 'the best debut professional mini golf performance in history.' Kirk recaps his day on the course with organizer Justin Pelletier and his mini golf rival Kyle Labrecque. Chris Klemmer tells us all about the pitch he sent to Big Cat in hopes of joining Barstool Sports full-time.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
dc:creator: Barstool Sports
